      "photos": [
        {
          "url": "images/sounds/resonanzraum-photo-1.png",
          "alt": "Live performance and recording at the house of Vita."
        },
        {
          "url": "images/sounds/resonanzraum-photo-2.png",
          "alt": "Live performance and recording at the house of Vita."
        }
      ],
      "bodyBlocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Live performance and recording at the house of Vita.\n\nThe house has its own tone and quiet history. Light, walls, and furniture hold the memory of earlier rehearsals. We work with this memory as a resonant body. We listen to how air, wood, and instruments react to each other and let the space decide when the piece begins and ends."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slug": "album-learning-to-breathe",
      "title": "learning to breathe",
      "year": 2025,
      "platform": "bandcamp",
      "cover": "images/covers/learning-to-breathe-cover.jpg",
      "embed": "https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/v=2/album=1109147001/size=large/tracklist=false/artwork=small/transparent=true/",
      "tracks": [],
      "meta": {
        "label": "Fish is watching",
        "platforms": [
          "Bandcamp"
        ]
      },
      "photos": [
        {
          "url": "images/sounds/learning-to-breathe-studio-1.jpg",
          "alt": "Studio view 1"
        },
        {
          "url": "images/sounds/learning-to-breathe-studio-2.jpg",
          "alt": "Studio view 2"
        }
      ],
      "bodyBlocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "This album charts a meditative journey through states of being, using sound as both compass and vessel. With layers of drones, pulses, and textured noise, it explores the interplay between stillness and motion, chaos and harmony, the internal and the external."
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "It begins with Learning to Breathe, a grounding meditation where heartbeat rhythms and noise textures invite the listener to rediscover the breath as a unifying force. Stream of Consciousness then drifts into the restless ebb and flow of thought, gradually aligning scattered currents into a flowing whole."
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "From there, Particle Flow propels the journey into a realm of kinetic energy—micro- and macro-pulses colliding, carrying the listener into a state of perpetual movement. Taken together, these pieces form a continuum of sound—inviting deep listening, in the subtle rhythms that underlie both mind and matter."
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "releases September 25, 2025"
        }
      ]
    },
